  "texts": [
    "This summary could highlight critical information such as diagnosis, prescribed medications and recommended treatments.",
    "It could also identify trends in the patient's health over time.",
    "By automating this process, healthcare providers could save time and ensure that nothing important is overlooked.",
    "Furthermore, these summaries could be used to improve communication between different healthcare providers and between providers and patients, as they provide a clear and concise overview of the patient's health status.",
    "The ability of LLMs to automate such processes can alleviate the current documentation burden and the consequent burnout many physicians across the world face [41]."
